<https://w3id.org/lmodel/fluxnova-bpm-platform/runtime/Incident> a sh:NodeShape ;
    rdfs:comment "An Incident represents a failure in the execution of a process instance. A possible failure could be for example a failed Job during the execution, so that the job retry is equal zero (job.retries ..." ;
